            "effect": "The aurosrath bellows a plea for gold, remarking that their foes are overladen. Creatures in a 15-foot emanation must succeed at a DC 19 Will save or become encumbered for 1 minute. The creature is aware that it can immediately end the condition by giving the aurosrath items or treasure worth at least 20 gp. Handing a held item to the aurosrath is a single Interact action. If the aurosrath\u2019s hands are full, the item falls in their space, but the condition still ends.",
