            "name": "Suffocating Wealth",
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "As the aurosrath holds their victim, the victim is smothered in a stream of phantom coins. A creature who begins its turn grabbed or restrained by an aurosrath can\u2019t speak and must hold its breath or it begins to suffocate. The coins produced are ephemeral and melt away to nothing when removed from the aurosrath\u2019s presence for more than 1 round.",
